@TemporalDashboard.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:8001

### Get all discovered workflows
GET {{TemporalDashboard.Api_HostAddress}}/api/workflows
Accept: application/json

### Get upload info
GET {{TemporalDashboard.Api_HostAddress}}/api/upload/info
Accept: application/json

### Get workflow diagrams for a DLL (replace {dllName} with actual DLL filename)
# GET {{TemporalDashboard.Api_HostAddress}}/api/workflows/{dllName}/diagrams
# Accept: application/json

###